42:44.311 --> 42:46.730
-Did you get my cards?
-Yes.

42:48.440 --> 42:51.860
Maybe it's not surprising
you respond to showmanship.

42:52.987 --> 42:55.573
Why do you want to see me, Ed?

42:57.533 --> 42:59.451
