43:00.035 --> 43:02.329
About us, I should say.

43:02.413 --> 43:04.498
The Atlanta Constitution?

43:04.582 --> 43:06.792
The story was picked up by the AP.

43:08.002 --> 43:11.463
-Oh.
-You said we were friends.

43:16.135 --> 43:18.304
-Yes.
-Are we friends, Holden?

43:19.013 --> 43:22.766
In the context of our work together, sure.

43:22.850 --> 43:24.268
Our work together.

43:24.893 --> 43:28.689
That's a nice way of putting it.
I'd categorize it the same way.

43:30.774 --> 43:33.110
And yet, our work is unfinished.

43:33.611 --> 43:36.322
-Okay.
-As I indicated in my letters.

43:37.031 --> 43:38.449
You have more...

43:40.034 --> 43:41.285
insights?

43:41.368 --> 43:42.202
I do.

43:44.038 --> 43:47.291
Well, I'm not going to trot them out
like some kind of show pony,

43:47.374 --> 43:50.085
especially when you've been talking
about me in my absence,

43:50.210 --> 43:53.213
using what I tell you
to legitimize yourself.

43:53.839 --> 43:55.382
That story was not...

43:58.302 --> 44:01.513
I... had had a bit to drink.

44:02.348 --> 44:05.643
What's this behavioral profiling
you're touting?

44:06.935 --> 44:07.936
Well...

44:12.691 --> 44:16.028
it's a way to determine
a criminal's psychology

44:16.111 --> 44:19.406
based on crime scenes
and personal characteristics.

44:19.490 --> 44:21.075
I love that.

44:23.327 --> 44:25.412
What's my psychology?

44:25.496 --> 44:27.498
I can't really tell you that.

44:27.581 --> 44:29.416
You can't or you won't?

44:29.500 --> 44:32.878
-It's shoptalk, Ed.
-My favorite.

44:33.754 --> 44:35.631
We're at an early point in the research.

44:35.714 --> 44:39.301
Not so early that you can't babble
about it in the press.

44:39.385 --> 44:42.971
And you pretty much admit
that I started you down this path.

44:43.055 --> 44:47.685
So... I believe you owe me
an explanation, Holden.

44:51.647 --> 44:54.233
You're what we'd call
an organized killer.

44:54.316 --> 44:55.442
Mm-hmm.

44:56.026 --> 44:58.821
Because of the extreme planning
that went into your crimes.

45:00.072 --> 45:02.241
