several times

45:02.324 --> 45:04.159
before selecting your first victim.

45:04.284 --> 45:05.411
You used your own vehicle

45:05.494 --> 45:07.871
both in the kidnapping
and disposing of the bodies.

45:08.664 --> 45:10.374
You followed your crimes in the media,

45:10.457 --> 45:13.794
which shows evidence
of continued fantasy.

45:14.962 --> 45:16.130
Mm-hmm.

45:18.590 --> 45:19.800
That's the gist.

45:20.300 --> 45:23.512
You think you can boil me down
to a single adjective?

45:23.595 --> 45:27.975
Of course not.
It's merely a way to sort characteristics.

45:28.058 --> 45:30.060
-You're an expert now.
-No.

45:30.644 --> 45:33.522
-Sounds like it.
-I am not an expert.

45:34.022 --> 45:36.108
But you want to be, don't you?

45:42.156 --> 45:43.365
Yes.

45:50.581 --> 45:53.125
Human blood is very hot.

45:53.625 --> 45:57.129
On a cold, humid morning
you can see it steam.

45:57.212 --> 45:59.047
What are you doing, Ed?

45:59.131 --> 46:01.925
Someone left a ballpoint pen
on my court file.

46:02.009 --> 46:03.927
I used the metal casing.

46:07.097 --> 46:08.849
Is this what you wanted to see?

46:10.225 --> 46:11.935
Why would I want to see that?

46:14.354 --> 46:16.064
Take a closer look.

46:22.070 --> 46:23.947
That's okay. Really.

46:28.494 --> 46:31.622
You know, women were initially
indifferent to me.

46:32.956 --> 46:35.209
They weren't interested in sharing.

46:37.002 --> 46:40.005
My whole life,
no one wanted to interact with me.

46:40.088 --> 46:42.966
Not even our cats, when I was a kid.

46:48.805 --> 46:50.057
